<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-blue-800 text-white section-padding">
  <div class="container mx-auto container-padding text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-heading mb-6 text-white leading-tight">
      Your Voice for a Better Healthcare System
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed opacity-95">
      We are dedicated to advocating for a healthcare system that is accessible, affordable, and equitable for all. Join us in making a difference.
    </p>
